<title>USA: Borealis names interim president/COO.</title>
<headline>Borealis names interim president/COO.</headline>
<dateline>INCLINE VILLAGE, Nev. 1997-01-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Borealis Technology Corp said it named an Peter Pitsker as its interim president and chief operating officer and has launched a search for a full-time president.</p>
<p>The company's founder and chairman Curtis Faith is relinquishing his title as president. Borealis' current chief operating officer, Rick Mellor, will &quot;remain with the company in an advisory capacity to the president,&quot; it said in a statement.</p>
<p>Pitsker has been on Borealis' board since September 1995. He was most recently chairman at Wonderware Corp.</p>
